    shabd:phraseIndex "1"^^xsd:integer ;
    shabd:phraseGurmukhi "ਭੁਖਿਆ ਭੁਖ"@pa ;
    shabd:phraseTransliteration "bhukẖiā bhukẖ"@en-Latn ;
    shabd:phraseGlossEn "the hunger of the hungry; those driven by craving"@en .

### Line 3 – Phrase 2: ਨ ਉਤਰੀ

